# Project Guardrails Template

## Change Scope
- Fix one issue at a time.
- Do not bundle unrelated fixes.

## Safety
- Prefer rollback-safe commits.
- Do not change core timing/constants without evidence.

## Validation
- Verify with real runtime checks before completion.
- For UI timing issues, test on at least two browsers.

## Communication
- Report commit hash, timestamp, and short reason.
